cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.CL

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on predicting content diffusion paths in mobile social networks.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper proposes a new deep neural network model for content popularity prediction.
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper deals with data transmission and traffic offloading in mobile networks.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a deep neural network model for prediction.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper deals with natural language processing in the context of social network data.
